    "en": {
      "title": "Monaragala girl kidnapped for sale rescued",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Wellawaya- A 5-year-old girl who went missing near the church gate on the 10th of this month has been found in the Bandarawela weekly market area.",
        "The person who took the girl to buy yogurt has also been arrested.",
        "A 25-year-old man from Tiyathala-Kuruthalawa area, who was working as a laborer at the house of the missing girl, has been arrested.",
        "The suspect took the girl from Wellawaya town to Bandarawela by bus and spent the night there at the weekly market.",
        "The next day, when she tried to go to her house in Kurdala, she was arrested by the police in the market area and the girl was also rescued.",
        "Initial investigations revealed that the suspect was ready to sell the girl for money."
      ],
